QuestData.Title: Leaving the Dream
QuestData.Description: Hold on tight, $n. The journey back to the waking world can be a little rough on unprepared minds and bodies.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Malfurion at the Eye of the Vortex in Darkshore.
QuestData.RewardText: You're just in time, $n. I don't know how much longer we can hold.
